<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />The voice of Yahweh is heard over the waters;</para>

<para style="q1">the God of glory thunders,</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh thunders over many waters.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />The voice of Yahweh is powerful;</para>

<para style="q1">the voice of Yahweh is majestic.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />The voice of Yahweh breaks the cedars;</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh breaks in pieces the cedars of Lebanon.</para>
